        {
          "id": "e046f60f-b51a-4732-8654-c4414da60e3c",
          "type": "h3",
          "indent": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "View Group"
            }
          ],
          "listStyleType": "decimal"
        },
        {
          "id": "517b9d59-4942-4e90-8b6c-732a6f9f9b27",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Settings > View Groups > + New"
            }
          ],
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "1."
        },
        {
          "id": "3992b3f1-a2a8-443d-b48f-e798dafabb3b",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Click the edit icon to change the view group name, icon and position in side panel; suggested name “Audit”"
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 2,
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "1."
        },
        {
          "id": "10808a27-0caa-4437-920d-a97c90b0576b",
          "type": "h3",
          "indent": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Saved Views"
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 2,
          "listStyleType": "decimal"
        },
        {
          "id": "c8cccc91-a6a4-442f-8969-ccf532afc0fc",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Add to search bar “tag:”Audit Blueprint\" to bring up all of the entities contained in this blueprint."
            }
          ],
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "2."
        },
        {
          "id": "21f7b3d5-2191-452a-8e0e-684a845c18f9",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 3,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "If desired, this can be saved through the panel at the top of the page, “Blueprint” or “All”."
            }
          ],
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "2.1."
        },
        {
          "id": "48b7d4b7-0bc2-432d-a6b4-acb73445a5b5",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Suggested Saved Views:"
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 2,
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "2."
        },
        {
          "id": "c1427f43-6650-4f4d-805a-b1f8b484c064",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 3,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Audit checklist templates, search for: “type:Audit Checklist”; suggested name of saved view “New”"
            }
          ],
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "2.2."
        },
        {
          "id": "a74b2c81-794e-4a6c-aab8-dd892edc5766",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 3,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "\"Audits\", search for: template:Internal Audit template:External Audit template:Regulatory Audit template:Supplier Audit "
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 2,
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "2.2."
        },
        {
          "id": "93ca7f41-ee3a-42fa-afad-6aaa88c03ec6",
          "type": "h3",
          "indent": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Audit SOP templates"
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 3,
          "listStyleType": "decimal"
        },
        {
          "id": "78a21eda-97b9-4bda-9b41-fd691aab35b2",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": " Audit SOP templates should all be updated to contain details specific to your company and its procedures."
            }
          ],
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "3."
        },
        {
          "id": "4e75cca4-4bc9-4056-bb26-6ff777ee69b1",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Select the SOP of interest, Make Changes > Go to change set > update the Upcoming Status Tag (i.e. Published) > Publish."
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 2,
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "3."
        },
        {
          "id": "4ced4b10-933a-47ff-85cd-da031f82090d",
          "type": "h3",
          "indent": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Customise Audit Forms (optional)"
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 4,
          "listStyleType": "decimal"
        },
        {
          "id": "81a26e41-8096-474f-9194-4c4245807fa0",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "From any of the templates (type:audit form), make changes to adapt templates to your existing processes by selecting “Make changes”, making the relevant edits, and then publishing a new version."
            }
          ],
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "4."
        },
        {
          "id": "b7ea573b-1aad-44fa-ba65-89c84afa4c19",
          "type": "h3",
          "indent": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Supplier Audits"
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 5,
          "listStyleType": "decimal"
        },
        {
          "id": "6ef56038-f585-4822-8a32-769b0f84ab0c",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Before completing the first Supplier Audit, you should ensure the Supplier had been logged in Seal using the Supplier Form, to ensure all related audits can be traced back to the same supplier."
            }
          ],
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "5."
        },
        {
          "id": "c2a05ae5-de0a-4583-9aa5-ca0c855d6c0e",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Select Supplier Form > New instance > complete necessary details"
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 2,
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "5."
        },
        {
          "id": "dd9fb08f-54aa-4d04-bfd5-b079acfc8869",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Configure Audit saved search within this instance if desired, search for template:Supplier Audit [supplier name], the audits will populate in this field over time, as they are created ."
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 3,
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "5."
        },
        {
          "id": "0a01260d-1d6f-4e2e-a77b-00c63457d873",
          "type": "p",
          "indent": 2,
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "> Go to change set > Publish"
            }
          ],
          "listStart": 4,
          "listStyleType": "decimal",
          "listParentIndex": "5."
        },
        {
          "id": "fe428cc0-a343-4169-805d-ef918d358076",
          "type": "p",
